title: MetaStreet DAO Liquidation Discount
body:
This is a NEGATIVE CONSENT vote - if a quorum of greater than 20% is reached, the proposal will be deemed to be denied by the DAO. If no quorum is reached, the proposal will be deemed to be accepted by the DAO.

Proposal: MetaStreet DAO will define "Liquidation Discount" as the estimated additional spread needed to cover liquidation costs in the event of default, (ie, transaction fees, holding costs, etc.). MetaStreet DAO will set this discount at 20%.
author: 0xC43A8A2530dCf66F458f7531a8275752d60f7689
